show.description: From a bullied schoolboy to a self-made millionaire — Karan’s journey is raw, emotional, and deeply inspiring. Witness how pain, rejection, and grit shape him into something extraordinary. A story of resilience that proves: your past doesn’t define your future. Watch Now !
